else is responsible for his bad mood.

68
00:02:34,540 --> 00:02:36,274
It's probably Boyle.

69
00:02:36,275 --> 00:02:39,711
Don't worry about it. Don't open it.

70
00:02:39,712 --> 00:02:40,745
